com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.builder
Interface IGeospatialPropertyValueBuilder.ISpatialReferenceAndValueBuilder

Enclosing interface:
IGeospatialPropertyValueBuilder
public static interface IGeospatialPropertyValueBuilder.ISpatialReferenceAndValueBuilder

A builder for creating machine-readable spatial reference values. Note: If this builder is not used, the default values for latitude and longitude will be zero.

Since:
4.0

                    double longitude)
Sets the machine-readable latitude and longitude of the geospatial value to the specified values.

Parameters:
latitude - The latitude, in units appropriate for the spatial reference system.

setSpatialReferenceSystem

void setSpatialReferenceSystem(String authority,
                               int id)
Sets the identifier (SRID) and issuing authority of the system in which the machine-readable spatial reference value is to be interpreted.

Parameters:
authority - A String containing the name of the issuing authority. This parameter must not be null or empty.
id - The identifier of the spatial reference system.
